# No secrets

- Do not commit `.env`, API keys, or webhook URLs with embedded tokens
- Use `VITE_*` env vars for client-side form endpoints (see `.env.example`)
- Do not hardcode Formspree/Netlify IDs in committed code — load from env when wired up
